
PROPOSED DOMAIN MODEL 

Class customer
	customer.see_menu
		display contents of the menu hash
	customer.place_order (item, quantity, price)
		takes item, quantity and sums them (by calling sum_total)
		returns hash with value as the total
	customer.verify_order
		
Class Restaurant
menu = {x:1, y:2, z:3}

	restaurant.sum_order

	restaurant.send_confirmation ()
